short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A collection of Webex tools and utilities

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An extension made to improve the UX of Webex by Cisco.

FEATURES:

- More playback speeds
- Better keyboard shortcuts - use jkl like in YouTube to skip 10s or pause/unpause the video, use arrow keys to skip 5s
- Zoom. Use the zoom icon to zoom inside the video. You can toggle it with ctrl+z and toggle follow mouse with z
